{"tid":1550594,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"喂,法律界 / 司法界 無野可以制止班賤種濫捕同暴打市民架咩?","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T16:55:53.000Z","uid":141656,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4733aa49b760b7e02b6fbbcc37f240a3ead94df5","tid":1550594,"uid":141656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:44:47.000Z","msg":"而家出街而家已經無自由<br />\n入機場食個飯,接個機都要比差佬逗<br />\n食完飯落街散個步又會遇到班喪犬<br />\n<br />\n一個唔好彩就比狗拉或者打到頭破血流<br />\n有無辦法做下野可以制止呢班人渣破壞社會安寧呀?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf4e8844d9f1db3f60ec23bd7dcf2d13ace8402","tid":1550594,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:45:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><di